#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:169 index.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid "Syntax"
msgstr "Sintaksa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalgebra; uses an intuitive algebraic syntax for entering user functions, "
"similar to that used on most modern graphing calculators. This section lists "
"the fundamental built-in operators available in &kalgebra;. The author of "
"&kalgebra; modeled this syntax after <ulink url=\"http://maxima.sourceforge."
"net/\">Maxima</ulink> and <ulink url=\"https://www.maplesoft.com/products/"
"maple/\">Maple</ulink> for users that may be familiar with these programs."
msgstr ""
"&kalgebra; uporablja intuitivno algebrsko sintakso za vnos uporabniških "
"funkcij, podobno tisti, ki se uporablja v večini sodobnih grafičnih računal. "
"V tem razdelku so navedeni temeljni vgrajeni operatorji, ki so na voljo v "
"programu &kalgebra;. Avtor programa &kalgebra; je to sintakso oblikoval po "
"<ulink url=\"http://maxima.sourceforge.net/\">Maxima</ulink> in <ulink url="
"\"https://www.maplesoft.com/products/maple/\">Maple</ulink> za uporabnike, "
"ki morda poznajo ta programa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For users that are interested in the inner workings of &kalgebra;, user "
"entered expressions are converted to &MathML; on the backend. A rudimentary "
"understanding of the capabilities supported by &MathML; will go a long way "
"toward revealing the inner capabilities of &kalgebra;."
msgstr ""
"Za uporabnike, ki jih zanima notranje delovanje sistema &kalgebra;, se "
"uporabniško vneseni izrazi v zaledju pretvorijo v &MathML;. Osnovno "
"razumevanje zmožnosti, ki jih podpira &MathML;, bo v veliki meri pomagalo "
"razkriti notranje zmožnosti &kalgebra;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here is a list of the available operators we have by now:"
msgstr "Tukaj je seznam operaterjev, ki so na voljo do zdaj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>+ - * / </literal>: Addition, subtraction, multiplication and "
"division."
msgstr ""
"<literal>+ - * / </literal>: seštevanje, odštevanje, množenje in deljenje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>^, ** </literal>: Power, you can use them both. Also it is possible "
"to use the unicode <literal>²</literal> characters. Powers are one way to "
"make roots too, you can do it like: <literal>a**(1/b)</literal>"
msgstr ""
"<literal>^, ** </literal>: Moč, lahko uporabite oba. Prav tako je mogoče "
"uporabiti unicode znake <literal>²</literal>. Tudi moči so eden od načinov "
"za ustvarjanje korenov, lahko naredite tako: <literal>a**(1/b)</literal>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>-&gt; </literal>: lambda. It is the way to specify one or more free "
"variables that will be bound in a function. For example, in the expression, "
"<userinput>length:=(x,y)->(x*x+y*y)^0.5</userinput>, the lambda operator is "
"used to denote that <literal>x</literal> and <literal>y</literal> will be "
"bound when the length function is used."
msgstr ""
"<literal>-&gt; </literal>: lambda. To je način za določitev ene ali več "
"prostih spremenljivk, ki bodo vezane v funkciji. Na primer, v izrazu "
"<userinput>dolžina:=(x,y)->(x*x+y*y)^0,5</userinput> je operator lambda "
"uporabljen za označevanje, da bosta <literal>x</literal> in <literal>y</"
"literal> pri uporabi funkcije dolžina povezana."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>x=a..b </literal>: This is used when we need to delimit a range "
"(bounded variable+uplimit+downlimit). This means that <literal>x</literal> "
"goes from <literal>a</literal> to <literal>b</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>x=a..b </literal>: Uporablja se, kadar moramo omejiti območje "
"(omejena spremenljivka+zgornjameja+spodnjameja). To pomeni, da <literal>x</"
"literal> pride od <literal>a</literal> do <literal>b</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>() </literal>: It is used to specify a higher priority."
msgstr "<literal>() </literal>: Uporablja se za določitev višje prioritete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>abc(params) </literal>: Functions. When the parser finds a "
"function, it checks if <literal>abc</literal> is an operator. If it is, it "
"will be treated as an operator, if it is not, it will be treated as a user "
"function."
msgstr ""
"<literal>abc(params) </literal>: Funkcije. Ko razčlenjevalnik najde "
"funkcijo, preveri, ali je <literal>abc</literal> operator. Če je, bo "
"obravnavan kot operator, če ni, bo obravnavan kot uporabniška funkcija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>:= </literal>: Definition. It is used to define a variable value. "
"You can do things like <userinput>x:=3</userinput>, <userinput>x:=y</"
"userinput> being <literal>y</literal> defined or not or <userinput>perimeter:"
"=r->2*pi*r</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>:= </literal>: Opredelitev. Uporablja se za določitev vrednosti "
"spremenljivke. Lahko naredite stvari, kot so <userinput>x:=3</userinput>, "
"<userinput>x:=y</userinput> je <literal>y</literal> določeno ali ne ali "
"<userinput>perimeter:=r->2*pi*r</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>? </literal>: Piecewise condition definition. Piecewise is the way "
"we can define conditional operations in &kalgebra;. Put another way, this is "
"a way of specifying an if, elseif, else condition. If we introduce the "
"condition before the '<literal>?</literal>' it will use this condition only "
"if it is true, if it finds a '<literal>?</literal>' without any condition, "
"it will enter in the last instance. Example: <userinput>piecewise { x=0 ? 0, "
"x=1 ? x+1, ? x**2 }</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<literal>? </literal>: Delna definicija pogoja. Po delih je način, kako "
"lahko definiramo pogojne operacije v &kalgebra;. Povedano drugače, to je "
"način določanja pogojev if, elseif, else. Če pred '<literal>?</literal>' "
"vpeljemo pogoj, bo ta pogoj uporabil le, če je resničen, če bo našel "
"'<literal>?</literal>' brez pogoja, bo vnesel zadnji primerek. Primer: "
"<userinput>piecewise { x=0 ? 0, x=1 ? x+1, ? x**2 }</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>{ } </literal>: &MathML; container. It can be used to define a "
"container. Mainly useful for working with piecewise."
msgstr ""
"<literal>{ } </literal>: &MathML; vsebnik. Uporablja se lahko za opredelitev "
"vsebnika. Uporabno predvsem za delo s kosi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>= &gt; &gt;= &lt; &lt;= </literal>: Value comparators for equal, "
"greater, greater or equal, less and less or equal respectively."
msgstr ""
"<literal>= &gt; &gt;= &lt; &lt;= </literal>: Primerjalniki vrednosti za "
"enako, večje, večje ali enako, manj in manj ali enako."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now you could ask me, why should the user mind about &MathML;? That’s easy. "
"With this, we can operate with functions like <function>cos()</function>, "
"<function>sin()</function>, any other trigonometrical functions, "
"<function>sum()</function> or <function>product()</function>. It does not "
"matter what kind it is. We can use <function>plus()</function>, "
"<function>times()</function> and everything which has its operator. Boolean "
"functions are implemented as well, so we can do something like "
"<function>or(1,0,0,0,0)</function>."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj bi me lahko vprašali, zakaj bi se moral uporabnik ukvarjati z &MathML;? "
"To je preprosto. S tem lahko operiramo s funkcijami, kot so <function>cos()</"
"function>, <function>sin()</function>, vse druge trigonometrične funkcije, "
"<function>sum()</function> ali <function>produkt()</function>. Ni pomembno, "
"kakšne vrste je. Uporabljamo lahko <function>plus()</function>, "
"<function>times()</function> in vse, kar ima svoj operator. Implementirane "
"so tudi logične funkcije, tako da lahko naredimo nekaj takega kot "
"<function>ali(1,0,0,0,0,0)</function>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Calculator"
msgstr "Uporaba računala"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalgebra;'s calculator is useful as a calculator on steroids. The user may "
"enter expressions for evaluation in <guimenu>Calculate</guimenu> or "
"<guimenu>Evaluate</guimenu> mode, depending on the <guimenu>Calculator</"
"guimenu> menu selection."
msgstr ""
"&kalgebra; računalo je uporaben kot kalkulator na steroidih. Uporabnik lahko "
"vnese izraze za vrednotenje v načinu <guimenu>Izračunaj</guimenu> ali "
"<guimenu>Ovrednoti</guimenu>, odvisno od izbire menija <guimenu>Računalo</"
"guimenu>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In evaluation mode &kalgebra; simplifies the expression even if it sees an "
"undefined variable. When in calculation mode &kalgebra;, calculates "
"everything and if it finds an undefined variable shows an error."
msgstr ""
"V načinu vrednotenja &kalgebra; poenostavi izraz, tudi če vidi nedefinirano "
"spremenljivko. Ko je v načinu izračuna &kalgebra;, izračuna vse in če najde "
"nedefinirano spremenljivko, pokaže napako."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition to displaying the user entered equations and results in the "
"Calculator display, all variables that are declared are displayed in a "
"persistent frame to the right. By double clicking on a variable you will see "
"a dialog that lets you change their values (just a way to trick the log)."
msgstr ""
"Poleg prikaza uporabnikovih vnesenih enačb in rezultatov na zaslonu računala "
"se vse deklarirane spremenljivke prikažejo v trajnem okvirju na desni "
"strani. Z dvojnim klikom na spremenljivko se prikaže pogovorno okno, v "
"katerem lahko spremenite njene vrednosti (to je le način, kako prevarati "
"dnevnik)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote><varname>ans</varname></quote> variable is special, every time "
"you enter an expression, the <quote><varname>ans</varname></quote> variable "
"value will be changed to the last result."
msgstr ""
"Spremenljivka <quote><varname>ans</varname></quote> je posebna, saj se ob "
"vsakem vnosu izraza vrednost spremenljivke <quote><varname>ans</varname></"
"quote> spremeni v zadnji rezultat."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following are example functions that can be entered in the input field "
"of the calculator window:"
msgstr ""
"V nadaljevanju so navedeni primeri funkcij, ki jih lahko vnesete v vnosno "
"polje okna računala:"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid "sin(pi)"
msgstr "sin(pi)"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid "k:=33"
msgstr "k:=33"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid "sum(k*x : x=0..10)"
msgstr "sum(k*x : x=0..10)"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "f:=p->p*k"
msgstr "f:=p->p*k"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid "f(pi)"
msgstr "f(pi)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following shows a screenshot of the calculator window after entering the "
"above example expressions:"
msgstr ""
"V nadaljevanju je prikazana slika okna računala po vnosu zgornjih primerov "
"izrazov:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of &kalgebra; calculator window with example expressions"
msgstr "Zaslonska slika okna &kalgebra; računala s primeri izrazov"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kalgebra; calculator window"
msgstr "&kalgebra; okno kalkulatorja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A user can control the execution of a series of calculations using the "
"<guimenu>Calculator</guimenu> menu options:"
msgstr ""
"Uporabnik lahko nadzoruje izvajanje niza izračunov z uporabo možnosti menija "
"<guimenu>Računalo</guimenu>:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>L</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Calculator</guimenu><guimenuitem>Load Script...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>L</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Računalo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Naloži skript...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Executes the instructions in a file sequentially. Useful if you want to "
"define some libraries or resume some previous work."
msgstr ""
"Zaporedno izvaja navodila v datoteki. Uporabno, če želite določiti nekatere "
"knjižnice ali nadaljevati prejšnje delo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Calculator</guimenu><guisubmenu>Recent Scripts</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Računalo</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nedavni skripti</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a submenu that will allow you to choose the recently executed "
"scripts."
msgstr "Prikaže podmeni, v katerem lahko izberete nedavno izvedene skripte."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>G</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Calculator</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Script...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>G</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Računalo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani Skript...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Saves the instructions you have typed since the session began to be able to "
"reuse. Generates text files so it should be easy to fix using any text "
"editor, like &kate;."
msgstr ""
"Shranite navodila, ki ste jih vnesli od začetka seje, da jih lahko ponovno "
"uporabite. Ustvari besedilne datoteke, tako da bi moralo biti enostavno "
"popraviti s katerim koli urejevalnikom besedila, kot &kate;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>S</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Calculator</guimenu><guimenuitem>Export Log...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>S</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Računalo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izvozi dnevnik...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Saves the log with all results into an &HTML; file to be able to print or "
"publish."
msgstr ""
"Dnevnik z vsemi rezultati shrani v datoteko &HTML;, ki jo lahko natisnete "
"ali objavite."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F3</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Calculator</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Insert ans...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F3</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Računalo</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Vstavi odg...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Insert the <quote><varname>ans</varname></quote> variable and makes it "
"easier to reuse older values."
msgstr ""
"Vstavi spremenljivko <quote><varname>ans</varname></quote> in olajša ponovno "
"uporabo starejših vrednosti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Calculator</guimenu><guimenuitem>Calculate</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Računalo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Računalo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A radio button to set the <guilabel>Execution Mode</guilabel> to calculation."
msgstr ""
"Radijski gumb za nastavitev <guilabel>Način izvajanja</guilabel> na "
"izračunaj."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Calculator</guimenu><guimenuitem>Evaluate</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Računalo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ovrednoti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A radio button to set the <guilabel>Execution Mode</guilabel> to evaluation."
msgstr ""
"Radijski gumb za nastavitev <guilabel>Način izvajanja</guilabel> na "
"ovrednoti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid "2D Graphs"
msgstr "2D Graf"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add a new 2D graph on &kalgebra;, select the <guilabel>2D Graph</"
"guilabel> tab and click the <guilabel>Add</guilabel> tab to add a new "
"function. Your focus will go to an input text box where you can type your "
"function."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati nov graf 2D v programu &kalgebra;, izberite zavihek "
"<guilabel>Graf 2D</guilabel> in kliknite zavihek <guilabel>Dodaj</guilabel>, "
"da dodate novo funkcijo. Osredotočili se boste na vnosno besedilno polje, v "
"katerega lahko vnesete svojo funkcijo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to use a typical <function>f(x)</function> function it is not "
"necessary to specify it, but if you want a <function>f(y)</function> or a "
"polar function, you will have to add <literal>y-&gt;</literal> and "
"<literal>q-&gt;</literal> as the bounded variables."
msgstr ""
"Če želite uporabiti tipično funkcijo <function>f(x)</function>, je ni treba "
"navesti, če pa želite funkcijo <function>f(y)</function> ali polarno "
"funkcijo, boste morali dodati <literal>y-&gt;</literal> in <literal>q-&gt;</"
"literal> kot omejeni spremenljivki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:363 index.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid "Examples:"
msgstr "Primeri:"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid "sin(x)"
msgstr "sin(x)"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>x²</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput>x²</userinput>"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid "y->sin(y)"
msgstr "y->sin(y)"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "q->3*sin(7*q)"
msgstr "q->3*sin(7*q)"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid "t->vector{sin t, t**2}"
msgstr "t->vector{sin t, t**2}"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have entered the function click on the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> "
"button to display the graph in the main window."
msgstr ""
"Če ste vnesli funkcijo, kliknite gumb <guibutton>OK</guibutton>, da se graf "
"prikaže v glavnem oknu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid "Features"
msgstr "Značilnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can set several graphs on the same view. Just use the <guilabel>Add</"
"guilabel> button when you are in List mode. You can set each graph its own "
"color."
msgstr ""
"V istem pogledu lahko nastavite več grafov. Ko ste v načinu seznama, "
"uporabite gumb <guilabel>Dodaj</guilabel>. Vsakemu grafu lahko nastavite "
"svojo barvo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The view can be zoomed and moved with the mouse. Using the wheel you can "
"zoom in and out. You can also select an area with the &LMB; and this area "
"will be zoomed in. Move the view with the keyboard arrow keys."
msgstr ""
"Pogled lahko povečate in premikate z miško. S kolescem lahko povečate in "
"pomanjšate velikost. Območje lahko izberete tudi z &LMB; in to območje bo "
"povečano. Pogled premikate s puščičnimi tipkami na tipkovnici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The viewport of 2D graphs can be explicitly defined using the "
"<guilabel>Viewport</guilabel> tab on a <guilabel>2D Graph</guilabel> tab."
msgstr ""
"Vidno polje za 2D-grafe lahko izrecno določite z zavihkom <guilabel>Vidno "
"polje</guilabel> na zavihku <guilabel>2D-graf</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>List</guilabel> tab at the bottom right part, you can open "
"an <guilabel>Editing</guilabel> tab to edit or remove a function with double-"
"click and check or uncheck the check box next to the function name to show "
"or hide it."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku <guilabel>Seznam</guilabel> v spodnjem desnem delu lahko odprete "
"zavihek <guilabel>Urejanje</guilabel>, da z dvojnim klikom uredite ali "
"odstranite funkcijo in potrdite ali odstranite potrditveno polje poleg imena "
"funkcije, da jo prikažete ali skrijete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid "In the <guimenu>2D Graph</guimenu> menu you find these options:"
msgstr "V meniju <guimenu>2D Graf</guimenu> so te možnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Grid</guimenuitem>: Show or hide the grid"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Mreža</guimenuitem>: Prikažite ali skrijte mrežo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Keep Aspect Ratio</guimenuitem>: Keep the aspect ratio while "
"zooming"
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Ohrani proporce</guimenuitem>: ohrani razmerje stranic med "
"povečavo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem>: Save (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo>) the graph as image file"
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Shrani</guimenuitem>: shrani (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo>) graf kot slikovno datoteko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:395
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Zoom in/out</guimenuitem>: Zoom in (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl; <keycap>+</keycap></keycombo>) and zoom out (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>-</keycap></keycombo>)"
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Približaj/Oddalji</guimenuitem>: Približaj (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>+</keycap></keycombo>) in oddalji (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>-</keycap></keycombo>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Actual Size</guimenuitem>: Reset the view to the original zoom"
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Prilagodi na dejansko velikost</guimenuitem>: Ponastavitev "
"pogleda na prvotno povečavo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Resolution</guilabel>: Followed by a list of radio buttons to "
"select a resolution for the graphs"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ločljivost</guilabel>: Sledi seznam radijskih gumbov za izbiro "
"ločljivosti grafov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below is a screenshot of a user who's cursor is at the rightmost root of the "
"function, <function>sin(1/x)</function>. The user who graphed it used very "
"fine resolution to make this graph (as it oscillates at higher and higher "
"frequency near the origin). There is also a live cursor feature where "
"whenever you move your cursor over a spot, it shows you the <literal>x</"
"literal> and <literal>y</literal> values in the bottom left corner of the "
"screen. A live <quote>tangent line</quote> is plotted on the function at the "
"live cursor location."
msgstr ""
"Spodaj je posnetek zaslona uporabnika, katerega kazalec je na skrajnem "
"desnem korenu funkcije <function>sin(1/x)</function>. Uporabnik, ki ga je "
"narisal, je pri izdelavi tega grafa uporabil zelo majhno ločljivost (saj "
"graf niha z vedno večjo frekvenco v bližini izvora). Na voljo je tudi "
"funkcija kurzorja v živo, ki vam ob vsakem premiku kurzorja nad točko v "
"spodnjem levem kotu zaslona prikaže vrednosti <literal>x</literal> in "
"<literal>y</literal>. Na funkciji na mestu kazalca v živo se izriše "
"<quote>tangentna črta</quote>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of &kalgebra; 2D Graph window"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona okna &kalgebra; 2D Graf"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:420
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kalgebra; 2D Graph window"
msgstr "&kalgebra; 2D graf okno"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:431
#, no-c-format
msgid "3D Graphs"
msgstr "3D Grafi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To draw a 3D graph with &kalgebra; select the <guilabel>3D Graph</guilabel> "
"tab and you will see an input field at the bottom where you will type your "
"function. <literal>Z</literal> cannot be defined yet. For the moment "
"&kalgebra; only supports 3D graphs explicitly dependent only on the "
"<literal>x</literal> and <literal>y</literal>, such as <userinput>(x,y)-"
">x*y</userinput>, where <userinput>z=x*y</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite s programom &kalgebra; narisati 3D-graf; izberite zavihek "
"<guilabel>3D-graf</guilabel> in na dnu boste videli vnosno polje, v katerega "
"boste vnesli svojo funkcijo. <literal>Z</literal> še ni mogoče določiti. Za "
"zdaj &kalgebra; podpira le 3D-grafe, ki so izrecno odvisni le od <literal>x</"
"literal> in <literal>y</literal>, na primer <userinput>(x,y)->x*y</"
"userinput>, kjer <userinput>z=x*y</userinput>."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid "(x,y)->sin(x)*sin(y)"
msgstr "(x,y)->sin(x)*sin(y)"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:443
#, no-c-format
msgid "(x,y)->x/y"
msgstr "(x,y)->x/y"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:446
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The view can be zoomed and moved with the mouse. Using the wheel you can "
"zoom in and out. Hold the &LMB; and move the mouse to rotate the graph."
msgstr ""
"Pogled lahko povečate in premikate z miško. S kolescem lahko povečate in "
"pomanjšate velikost. Držite &LMB; in premikajte miško, da zavrtite graf."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &Left; and &Right; arrow keys rotate the graph around the <literal>z</"
"literal> axis, the &Up; and &Down; arrow keys rotate around the horizontal "
"axis of the view. Press <keycap>W</keycap> to zoom in the plot and "
"<keycap>S</keycap> to zoom it out."
msgstr ""
"Puščični tipki &Left; in &Right; vrtita graf okoli <literal>z</literal> osi, "
"puščični tipki &Up; in &Down; pa se vrtita okoli vodoravne osi prikaza. "
"Pritisnite <keycap>W</keycap> za povečavo ploskve in <keycap>S</keycap> za "
"njeno pomanjšanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid "In the <guimenu>3D Graph</guimenu> menu you find these options:"
msgstr "V meniju <guimenu>3D Graf</guimenu> so te možnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:456
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem>: Save (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo>) the graph as image file or supported document"
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Shrani</guimenuitem>: shrani (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo>) graf kot slikovno datoteko ali podprt dokument"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Reset View</guimenuitem>: Reset the view to the original zoom "
"in the <guimenu>3D Graph</guimenu> menu"
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Ponastavi pogled</guimenuitem>: Ponastavitev pogleda na prvotno "
"povečavo v meniju <guimenu>3D Graf</guimenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can draw the graphs with <guimenuitem>Dots</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Lines</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Solid</guimenuitem> styles "
"in the <guimenu>3D Graph</guimenu> menu"
msgstr ""
"V meniju <guimenuitem>3D Graf</guimenuitem> lahko narišete grafe s slogi "
"<guimenuitem>Pike</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Črte</guimenuitem> ali "
"<guimenuitem>Polno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below is a screenshot of the so-called <quote>sombrero</quote> function. "
"This particular graph is shown using the 3D graph line-style."
msgstr ""
"Spodaj je posnetek zaslona tako imenovane funkcije <quote>sombrero</quote>. "
"Ta graf je prikazan v slogu črt 3D-grafa."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of &kalgebra; 3D Graph window"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona okna &kalgebra; 3D Graf"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kalgebra; 3D Graph window"
msgstr "&kalgebra; okno 3D grafa"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dictionary"
msgstr "Slovar"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The dictionary provides a list of all &kalgebra; built in functions. It can "
"be used to find the definition of an operation and its input parameters. "
"It's a useful place to go to find the many capabilities of &kalgebra;."
msgstr ""
"Slovar vsebuje seznam vseh &kalgebra; vgrajenih funkcij. Z njim lahko "
"poiščete opredelitev operacije in njene vhodne parametre. To je koristen "
"kraj, kjer lahko najdete številne zmožnosti &kalgebra;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below is a screenshot of the &kalgebra; dictionary lookup of the cosine "
"function."
msgstr ""
"Spodaj je posnetek zaslona, ki prikazuje iskanje funkcije kosinusa v "
"slovarju &kalgebra;."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of the &kalgebra; dictionary window"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona okna slovarja &kalgebra;"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:501
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kalgebra; dictionary window"
msgstr "&kalgebra; slovarsko okno"

